title: Futurama S07E16 T, The Terrestrial
description:
Futurama - Season 7 - Episode 16 
---------------------------------

Futurama follows the life of Philip J. Fry, a pizza delivery boy who accidentally
stumbles into a freezer on December 31, 1999 and wakes up a thousand years later.
In his future home of New New York City, Fry goes to work for the Planet Express
Intergalactic delivery company, where he befriends Bender, a booze-fueled robot,
and sets his romantic sights on Leela, a sexy cyclops who enjoys beating him up.

Produced by The Curiosity Company and 20th Century Fox Television.


After being marooned on an distant planet, Fry is befriended by a young monster.
